readability_reflection: Overall I found string interpolation more readable. I was able to tell the spacing of the strings more clearly.
comprehension_debugging: A bit , when using string concatenation I would often have to check multiple time just to make sure the spacing was correct.
preference_rationale: Overall I think I would choose interpolation, its much more easily readable compared to string concatenation despite me having been more used to using concatenation.
learning_curve: I more used to concatenation since that what i learned early on but throughout the survey I felt more comfortable overtime with interpolation despite being less accustom to using it.
